## FAQs
How is my data stored?
![Expand](https://camelai.com/assets/images/chevron-up-white.png)
camelAI's infrastructure is hosted on AWS. Data from applications is pulled only when necessary and limited to what you request in your prompt. It is stored in an EC2 cache for 5 minutes and then deleted. For more information, please see our [Security Policy](https://camelai.com/</security>) and our [security blog post](https://camelai.com/<https:/camelai.com/blog/FAQ-security/>).
Do you train on my data?
![Expand](https://camelai.com/assets/images/chevron-up-white.png)
No, we do not train on your data. CamelAI is powered by OpenAI's API. We have opted out of data sharing for training. You can read more about OpenAI's API policies [here](https://camelai.com/<https:/openai.com/enterprise-privacy/>).
Are my app connections secure?
![Expand](https://camelai.com/assets/images/chevron-up-white.png)
Yes, your app connections are secure. We use OAuth 2.0 when available or secure key authentication to authenticate and authorize access to your applications. Your data is encrypted in transit and at rest. If you revoke access to an app, the connection is immediately destroyed and we will no longer have access to that application.
How do you pull my data?
![Expand](https://camelai.com/assets/images/chevron-up-white.png)
camelAI only communicates with your connected apps when you request data in the chat. We do not train on your data, nor do we access or store any data without your request and supervision.

### camelAI: Your Data, Powered by AI

Founded in 2023 and based in Austin, TX, camelAI aims to transform how businesses utilize their data through advanced AI-powered insights. Backed by Y Combinator's Batch W24, camelAI offers a **business intelligence agent** that promises **actionable insights in minutes**—no coding or SQL knowledge required.

At its core, camelAI is a data analyst that connects seamlessly to a variety of data sources, including CSVs, CRMs, SQL databases, and data warehouses. This flexibility allows users to ask complex questions and get instant reports, charts, and dashboards, unlocking the power of their data in a way that's intuitive and efficient.

#### Key Highlights:
- **Team**: Currently a small but focused team of three.
- **Mission**: To deliver quick, actionable insights through an AI-driven interface that empowers users without technical expertise.
- **Founder Support**: Led by Tom Blomfield, notable in the startup landscape, providing strategic guidance.
- **Focus Areas**: Operates under several tagging categories including SaaS, data science, data visualization, and AI—all buzzing topics right now.

With camelAI, businesses can:
- **Interact with live data**: Ask questions and get immediate visualizations tailored to their needs.
- **Create powerful dashboards**: Save graphs and revisit live data whenever necessary.
- **Ensure security and privacy**: With a commitment to data integrity, camelAI does not train on user data, and utilizes AWS for secure application integration.

Want to see it in action? You can start with a free trial or book a demo to explore how camelAI can streamline your data analytics process.

For more information and to get started, visit [camelAI's website](https://camelai.com/). 

So, why not let your data do the heavy lifting? With camelAI, you're not just analyzing data, you're unleashing its potential!
